{"article_id":"D7IDpK754A0mARNM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"North Korea and the US have given differing accounts","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"of why the second summit between Donald Trump and Kim Jong-un ended in failure on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"The abrupt end to the Hanoi meeting ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"which was cut short by several hours ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"was a setback from both leaders","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"who had made long journeys","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"- Kim by rail and Trump by air -","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"in the expectation","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that a deal was within reach .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"There are no plans for a third summit ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"but the US has expressed willingness to continue talks at a lower level .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"In his version of events , Trump said","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"the deal had broken down","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"because Kim wanted complete sanctions relief","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"for dismantling the main nuclear complex at Yongbyon ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"but the US wanted other nuclear facilities ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"including covert sites ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"disabled as well .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" It was about the sanctions basically , \"","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Trump said at a press conference in Hanoi .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"\" They wanted the sanctions lifted in their entirety","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"and we couldn ' t do that ...","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Sometimes you have to walk ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and this was just one of those times . \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Play Video 1:25","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Trump-Kim nuclear talks in Hanoi break down - video report","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"\" There is a gap .","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"We have to have sanctions , \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"\" There is a gap .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"We have to have sanctions","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"and he wants to denuke .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"But he wants to just do areas","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that are less important","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"than the areas","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that we want . \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"North Korea disputed Trump ' s explanation .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"At abruptly scheduled midnight press conference in Hanoi , the North Korean foreign minister , Ri Yong Ho , said","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Pyongyang had only demanded partial sanctions relief in return","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"for closing Yongbyon .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"the US had wasted an opportunity","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that \" may not come again \"","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and Pyongyang ' s position would not change","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"even if the US seeks further talks .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Trump however made clear","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that the status quo will continue ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"with North Korea continuing to suspend nuclear and missile tests ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"while the US will not take part in joint military exercises with South Korea ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"which the US president is opposed to anyway .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"\" I gave that up quite a while ago","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"because it costs us $ 100m","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"to do it .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"I hated to see it .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"I thought","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"it was unfair , \"","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"that South Korea should shoulder more of the costs .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" Exercising is fun","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"and it ' s nice they play their war games .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"I ' m not saying","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"its not necessary .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"On some levels it is .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"On other levels it ' s not . \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"On Friday , South Korea ' s president , Moon Jae-in , used a national holiday speech","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"to try to ease any disappointment .","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"\" I believe","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"this is part of a process","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"to reach a higher level of agreement .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Now our role has become even more important , \"","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"\" My administration will closely communicate and cooperate with the United States and North Korea","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"so as to help their talks reach a complete settlement by any means . \"","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"In a press conference","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"after the talks broke down ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Trump remained protective of the North Korean leader and the relationship between the two men .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"\" We spent all day with Kim Jong-un , \"","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"\" He ' s quite a guy and quite a character .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"And our relationship is very strong . \"","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Play Video 0:34","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"Kim Jong-un answers question from foreign journalist for first time - video","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"He even defended Kim over the death of the US student Otto Warmbier ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"who was sent home from North Korea seriously ill in June 2017 .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"\" He says","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"he didn ' t know about it","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"and I will take him at his word , \"","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Trump gave the most detailed public account to date of the central disagreements","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"that have dogged the negotiations .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"He confirmed","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that the US side had confronted Pyongyang with US intelligence about covert nuclear facilities outside Yongbyon","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and demanded","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"they be put on the negotiating table .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"\" We know the country very well , every inch of that country , \"","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"adding","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"that Yongbyon , \" while very big ,","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"wasn ' t enough \" .","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"\" We had to have more than that ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"because there were other things","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"that we haven ' t talked about ,","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"that we found ,","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"that we found a long time ago ,","depth":16},{"id":105,"text":"but people didn ' t know about , \"","depth":16},{"id":106,"text":"he went on ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"making clear","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"that one of the sites","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"he was talking about","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"was a second covert uranium enrichment programme .","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"\" We brought many points up","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"they were surprised","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"that we knew . \"","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"relaxing all sanctions in return for Yongbyon would been meant giving up leverage","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"\" that has taken so long to build . \"","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"The collapse of the two leaders ' talks came suddenly .","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"Late on Wednesday night the White House circulated detailed plans for negotiating sessions , a working lunch and a signing ceremony for a joint agreement .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"When the two leaders reconvened on Thursday morning , however ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"they appeared sombre and cautious","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"about whether a deal was possible .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"A few hours later , the summit was called off .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"The signing ceremony was cancelled","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"and the official lunch left uneaten .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Table settings and name cards went unused in the empty dining hall of the Metropole Hotel , the summit venue ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"as the leaders made their way back to their own hotels .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"The US secretary of state , Mike Pompeo , said","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"the breakdown of talks was partly caused by differences over the sequences of nuclear disarmament and sanctions relief .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"The US wanted North Korea to put its current arsenal ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"thought to consist of several dozen warheads , some mounted on missiles ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"on the negotiating table as well ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"nuclear negotiations would resume quickly ,","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"although no new meetings have yet been scheduled .","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"Trump flew out of Hanoi in the late afternoon ,","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"while Kim stayed in the city for talks with the Vietnamese leadership","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"and will make the 70-hour car and train journey back to Pyongyang at the weekend .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"It was unclear whether he would stop in Beijing","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"to meet the Chinese president , Xi Jinping .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"he would call his regional allies , the Japanese prime minister , Shinzo Abe , and the South Korean president , Moon Jae-in ,","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"as soon as he boarded Air Force One .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"The breakdown of the summit is a political disaster for Moon ,","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"who had been counting on progress","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"that would lift international sanctions","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"restricting trade and investment between North and South Korea .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"A South Korean diplomat said","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"Seoul was stunned by the result .","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"\" It was shock .","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"We are trying to figure out what happened , \"","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"the diplomat said .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"\" We need to watch what happened behind the scenes . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":311,"left":220,"right":310,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":220,"left":179,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":166,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":164,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":157,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":163,"left":158,"right":162,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":160,"right":161,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":4,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":172,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left